metadata.name: THE HEALER
metadata.description:
"Many things happened last year that make me feel so exhausted.
I hope this Ox year will let me rest a bit more and heal me up."

Illustration for "Dear Year of Ox, Please BE KIND." The project that I had a collaboration with the eID team.

This project lets artists from different countries and regions express their wishes and hopes for the year of ox with their works, and sent a positive message to the world.
